title: Dock Price Reaches $0.14 on Exchanges (DOCK)
content: Dock (CURRENCY:DOCK) traded 19.8% higher against the U.S. dollar during the twenty-four hour period ending at 17:00 PM E.T. on June 2nd. In the last week, Dock has traded up 16% against the U.S. dollar. One Dock token can now be bought for $0.14 or 0.00001771 BTC on major exchanges including Gate.io, Kucoin and IDEX. Dock has a total market capitalization of $30.89 million and approximately $6.15 million worth of Dock was traded on exchanges in the last day.    Here’s how other cryptocurrencies have performed in the last day:    Ripple (XRP) traded 4.3% higher against the dollar and now trades at $0.64 or 0.00008407 BTC.  Stellar (XLM) traded up 4.2% against the dollar and now trades at $0.30 or 0.00003914 BTC.  IOTA (MIOTA) traded up 0.9% against the dollar and now trades at $1.89 or 0.00024749 BTC.  TRON (TRX) traded 5.3% higher against the dollar and now trades at $0.0610 or 0.00000799 BTC.  NEO (NEO) traded 3.8% higher against the dollar and now trades at $56.56 or 0.00740923 BTC.  Tether (USDT) traded down 1.1% against the dollar and now trades at $0.99 or 0.00012957 BTC.  VeChain (VEN) traded 9.5% higher against the dollar and now trades at $3.72 or 0.00048676 BTC.  Binance Coin (BNB) traded up 4.8% against the dollar and now trades at $14.71 or 0.00192636 BTC.  Ontology (ONT) traded up 10.4% against the dollar and now trades at $7.77 or 0.00101838 BTC.  Zilliqa (ZIL) traded up 7.7% against the dollar and now trades at $0.12 or 0.00001554 BTC.   Dock Token Profile     Dock launched on January 17th, 2018. Dock’s total supply is 1,000,000,000 tokens and its circulating supply is 228,550,076 tokens. Dock’s official Twitter account is @dock_io . The Reddit community for Dock is /r/dockio . Dock’s official message board is medium.com/dock-io . The official website for Dock is dock.io .  Dock Token Trading    Dock can be purchased on these cryptocurrency exchanges: Kucoin, IDEX and Gate.io. It is usually not presently possible to purchase alternative cryptocurrencies such as Dock directly using US dollars. Investors seeking to trade Dock should first purchase Bitcoin or Ethereum using an exchange that deals in US dollars such as Gemini, Changelly or GDAX. Investors can then use their newly-acquired Bitcoin or Ethereum to purchase Dock using one of the aforementioned exchanges.
